data.title: Dodge Riverside Golf Club
data.meta_description: Dodge Riverside Golf Club is found along the Missouri River and provides outstanding views of the Omaha Metro. Located just minutes from downtown Omaha.
data.text:
Nestled along the scenic Missouri River, Dodge Riverside Golf Club offers breathtaking views of the Omaha Metro area. Conveniently located just minutes from downtown Omaha, this premier golfing destination features an 18-hole, par 72 course that boasts a perfect blend of beauty and challenge. Dodge Riverside is renowned for its 6,400 yards of subtle, rolling terrain, making it the ideal walking golf course in the Council Bluffs/Omaha region.

At Dodge Riverside Golf Club, we pride ourselves on fostering a welcoming atmosphere, complete with outstanding food and drink options at the Riverside Grille. Our course is designed to encourage walking, offering close proximity from green to tee, and we invite golfers of all skill levels to enjoy a truly enjoyable walking experience.
